tachyon.shell.command

Class AbstractTfsShellCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.shell.command.AbstractTfsShellCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TfsShellCommand
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractAclCommand, CopyFromLocalCommand, CopyToLocalCommand, CountCommand, CreateLineageCommand, DeleteLineageCommand, GetCapacityBytesCommand, GetUsedBytesCommand, ListLineagesCommand, LoadMetadataCommand, MkdirCommand, MountCommand, MvCommand, PersistCommand, SetTtlCommand, TouchCommand, UnmountCommand, UnsetTtlCommand, WithWildCardPathCommand

    public abstract class AbstractTfsShellCommand
extends Object
implements TfsShellCommand
    The base class for all the TfsShellCommand classes. It provides a default argument validation method and a place to hold the FileSystem client.
